<title>LogSvc Class Reference</title>
<indexterm><primary>LogSvc</primary></indexterm>
<para>

<para>The <link linkend="_class_log_svc">LogSvc</link> class is responsible for logging messages. This is a thread-safe class that offloads messages to a ring buffer and then logs them to the console or another dstination. </para>
 
</para>
